---
// Contact CTA block
---

<section id="contact" class="bg-paper py-16 md:py-24 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-10">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="small-caps text-copper mb-5 text-center" data-reveal>The invitation</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-[9vw] md:text-[5.5rem] lg:text-[6.5rem] text-ink leading-[0.95] text-center mb-8 md:mb-10" data-reveal>
        Let's <span class="italic font-display-italic text-copper">talk</span>.
      </h2>

      <p class="text-ink-soft text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 md:mb-12" data-reveal>
        The best way to start is a short email. Tell me what's going on at your executive office, whether you're thinking hire or fractional, and what a great outcome would look like in the first 90 days.
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-8 mb-16" data-reveal>
        <a
          href="mailto:lmartinlapc@gmail.com?subject=Working%20with%20you%20as%20our%20EA&body=Hi%20Leigh-Ann%2C%20%0A%0AI%27m%20reaching%20out%20about%20...%0A"
          class="group bg-ink text-paper p-8 md:p-10 rounded-sm hover:bg-copper transition-colors flex flex-col"
        >
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6">
            <span class="small-caps text-paper/40 group-hover:text-paper/60">Primary</span>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-paper/40 group-hover:text-paper group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-all" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"/></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl text-paper leading-tight mb-4">Email me directly</p>
          <p class="font-mono text-sm text-paper/80 tabular mb-2">lmartinlapc@gmail.com</p>
          <p class="text-paper/50 text-sm mt-auto pt-6">I reply within one business day.</p>
        </a>

        <a
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/leigh-ann-martin"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          class="group border-2 border-ink p-8 md:p-10 rounded-sm hover:bg-ink hover:text-paper transition-colors flex flex-col"
        >
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6">
            <span class="small-caps text-ink-muted group-hover:text-paper/60">Secondary</span>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-ink-muted group-hover:text-paper group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-all" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"/></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl text-ink group-hover:text-paper leading-tight mb-4">Find me on LinkedIn</p>
          <p class="font-mono text-sm text-ink/70 group-hover:text-paper/80 tabular mb-2">linkedin.com/in/leigh-ann-martin</p>
          <p class="text-ink-muted group-hover:text-paper/50 text-sm mt-auto pt-6">Recommendations, posts, and a deeper career archive live there.</p>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Closing editorial ornament -->
      <div class="flex items-center gap-6 justify-center pt-10 border-t border-rule" data-reveal>
        <div class="w-12 h-px bg-ink"></div>
        <span class="font-display-italic text-2xl text-copper tracking-wide">fin.</span>
        <div class="w-12 h-px bg-ink"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
